## Your job

Answer the ticket's Question with receipts. Sources:

- pi extension API types: `~/Code/joelhooks/pi-mono/packages/coding-agent/src/core/extensions/types.ts`
- Emission sites: `~/Code/joelhooks/pi-mono/packages/coding-agent/src/core/agent-session.ts` (see the `agent_end` / `turn_end` emit paths and the retry logic around them)
